<SYNC Start=933345><P Class=KRCC>
응?
<SYNC Start=934356><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=938977><P Class=KRCC>
이건...
<SYNC Start=940123><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=943180><P Class=KRCC>
