<SYNC Start=1007844><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1024755><P Class=KRCC>
무슨 말을 하고 싶은거야!
<SYNC Start=1026513><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1029683><P Class=KRCC>
알았어
<SYNC Start=1030834><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1035694><P Class=KRCC>
