<SYNC Start=1038198><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1041331><P Class=KRCC>
아가씨
<SYNC Start=1042949><P Class=KRCC>
저에요
<SYNC Start=1044518><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1047284><P Class=KRCC>
