<SYNC Start=1167110><P Class=KRCC>
신이치씨
<SYNC Start=1169745><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1175417><P Class=KRCC>
죄송해요
<SYNC Start=1177334><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1192309><P Class=KRCC>
정말로 잘 어울리세요
<SYNC Start=1194706><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1199228><P Class=KRCC>
아름다우십니다
<SYNC Start=1200853><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1220400><P Class=KRCC>
다녀왔어~
<SYNC Start=1221367><P Class=KRCC>
선물 사왔다~
<SYNC Start=1222539><P Class=KRCC>
어머나
<SYNC Start=1223504><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1226000><P Class=KRCC>
너희들
<SYNC Start=1227421><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1228422><P Class=KRCC>
방해했나?
<SYNC Start=1230379><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1233184><P Class=KRCC>
